!begin_node (!kw [no_8bit])
!html_name cmd_no_8bit

Do not use special characters.

!begin_xlist [(!TYPEPOSITION)]

!item [(!TYPEPOSITION)] (!SWITCH), (!PREAMBLE)

!item [(!SYNTAX)] (!T)!/no_8bit [(!FORMAT)](!t)

!item [(!DESCRIPTION)]
Switches off the usage of German umlauts. The example shows how to
switch it off when converting to a manualpage. Umlauts are then
replaced by ae, oe, ue, ss, Ae, Oe and Ue.

!item [(!EXAMPLE)]
(!T)!/no_8bit [man](!t)

!item [(!SEEALSO)]
(!link [Special characters] [Special characters]), (!KW [no_umlaute])

!end_xlist

!end_node
